In this video, I will take you guys through the warp section of Serum 2 where you will find frequency modulation (FM), FM warp, phase distortion (PD) warp, ring modulation (RM), and amplitude modulation (AM). We can use these to add even more harmonics and create more interesting sounds complex sounds .
